import React from 'react';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import InputGroup from 'react-bootstrap/InputGroup';

export class HostForm2 extends React.Component{
    constructor(props){
      super(props);
    }

    render(){

      return(
        <Form>
        <Form.Row>
          <Form.Group controlId="formSpaceType">
            <Form.Label>what type of space is this?</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control as="select" multiple>
                <option>Garage</option>
                <option>Closet</option>
                <option>Basement</option>
                <option>Attic</option>
                <option>Outdoor Storage (i.e. shed)</option>
                <option>other</option>
              </Form.Control>
          </Form.Group>
          </Form.Row>
          <Form.Row>
            <InputGroup className="mb-3">
                <Form.Group controlId="formSpaceAvailable">
                  <Form.Control type="dimensions" placeholder="23.5" />
                </Form.Group>

                x
                <Form.Group controlId="formSpaceAvailable">
                  <Form.Control type="dimensions" placeholder="23.5" />
                </Form.Group>
                x
                <Form.Group controlId="formSpaceAvailable">
                  <Form.Control type="dimensions" placeholder="23.5" />
                </Form.Group>
                <InputGroup.Append>
                  <InputGroup.Text>ft^3</InputGroup.Text>
                </InputGroup.Append>

            </InputGroup>
          </Form.Row>
          <Form.Row>
            <InputGroup className="mb-3">
              <InputGroup.Prepend id="col"as={Form.Col}>
                <InputGroup.Text>$</InputGroup.Text>
              </InputGroup.Prepend>

              <Form.Group id="col"as={Form.Col} controlId="formPricePerSq">
                <Form.Control type="price" placeholder="5.00" />
              </Form.Group>

              <InputGroup.Append id="col"as={Form.Col}>
                <InputGroup.Text>per sq. foot</InputGroup.Text>
              </InputGroup.Append>
            </InputGroup>
          </Form.Row>

          <Form.Row>
            <Form.Group controlId="formStorageNotes">
              <Form.Control as="textarea" rows="3" placeholder="anything else to note about the space?"/>
            </Form.Group>
          </Form.Row>
        </Form>


      );
    }
  }

  export default HostForm2;
